Title: Culling the Swarm
Description:
The Empress continues to amass her forces. Without intervention, they WILL overrun that wall - even if it means smothering it in the corpses of a million swarmborn.

Let us find a better place for those corpses.

Let me know when you are ready to depart for the clutches - I will gladly drop you in from above.
ObjectivesText: Slay 40 Shek'zeer Mantid in the Clutches of Shek'zeer. Speak with Kil'ruk the Wind-Reaver for an air-drop.
